{"tid":1492120,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"代轉 825 家屬連線 還警於民 集會","createTime":"2019-08-20T16:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T01:23:54.000Z","uid":284925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a54d70d4aba55f33f78d76846e387ad1006697d2","tid":1492120,"uid":284925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UyzyRi7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUyzyRi7.jpg&h=424c5949&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTv985P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTv985P.jpg&h=23ca47a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m3RxnqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm3RxnqQ.jpg&h=f1f1ad63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>家屬連線 還警於民 集會</strong><br />\n-<br />\n主題：還警於民<br />\n日期：25/8<br />\n地點：中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n時間：下午2:00開始<br />\n集會過後，我們會由親屬步行至警總及特首辦遞交請願信。<br />\n*我們正向警方申請不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n我們深愛我們任職警員的家人，當初他們投身警隊，是因為一份熱愛正義的心，希望警惡懲奸，維護法治，保護市民。但現在因為政治問題迫不得已與市民對峙，已令他們心酸不已，加上警隊行動策劃不善，個別前線警員處理手法問題，令警民關係墮入深淵。<br />\n<br />\n現在能挽救殘局的方法，只有政府聆聽市民心聲及成立獨立調查委員會，懲治手法不當的人，更為盡職的警員平反。<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我們的五項訴求:<br />\n<br />\n1.政治問題政治解決，特首應盡快與其班子積極討論市民訴求的可行性；<br />\n<br />\n2. 呼籲警隊高層制定一套適合於處理現時示威者的行動手法；嘗試使用不同方式處理示威遊行；減少衝突；<br />\n<br />\n3. 促請成立市民與警員真誠溝通的平台；修補撕裂；<br />\n<br />\n4. 懇請前線警察刻己自律，以不徇私的公平手法執法，以保護市民為首要任務；<br />\n<br />\n5. 成立全面獨立調查委員會，徹查運動至今所牽涉的各方因素。<br />\n<br />\n我們希望邀請與我們理念相同的警員親屬，以至市民參與。<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n如有興趣在集會期間提供協助請INBOX與負責人聯絡。另外我們亦希望邀請家屬及市民在集會中分享心聲，有意也請INBOX我們。<br />\n<br />\n更多集會內容將稍後公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOur FB link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PoliceRelativesConnection/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPoliceRelativesConnection%2F&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41Ap4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=e25cb9bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PoliceRelativesConnection/</a><br />\nTG Link: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/RelativesConnectionGathering\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FRelativesConnectionGathering&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41Ap4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=f3eb9798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/RelativesConnectionGathering</a><br />\n<br />\n#還市民真警察<br />\n#給彼此一個機會<br />\n#我們願意成為市民與警隊之間的橋樑<br />\n#用行動喚醒警隊初心<br />\n#對的人不壓迫<br />\n#錯的人不姑息<br />\n#ReturnPoliceToPeople<br />\n#BridgeBetweenPeoplePolice"},{"pid":"a383f2b1590b3dfc72c8fe2628691fd43a037cd3","tid":1492120,"uid":101498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:39:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">今晚元朗靜坐</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/grVupum.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgrVupum.png&h=403be7d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></div></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b62427bdc16fced645d986885285d9e67ef4aa","tid":1492120,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:40:32.000Z","msg":"開始驚有報應？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6ee2ca52916ffc74717babc92702d85c8c8e22","tid":1492120,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"23778d60823a74369c1fb8a4359afca43701dfde","tid":1492120,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:12:23.000Z","msg":"會比休班狗影相同毆打，不了"},{"pid":"d157de6a0fe1b492c01762aa970882b15a57bd9f","tid":1492120,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:23:54.000Z","msg":"如果呢個集會有國安入去影鳩D家屬大頭就好笑<br />\nmon post嘅黑警小心d老婆仔女比人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}